They think stupid intuitive actions like putting brackets (in the wr...Full ReviewAfter a long search I finally got the kind of calculator that I wanted. I think it may the best calculator app right now especially with most others trying to sell paid versions while their apps are getting even dumber than before. They think stupid intuitive actions like putting brackets (in the wrong places), and a fancy look will make their app worth selling. I got so fed up trying out those worthless calculators. Thank god that I stumbled upon this app. It is the most logical calculator just like the Casio calculator with same model number which I am very used to. Good job developers! I would like to buy add free version.
